      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk a migraine seems way too sudden for that. it was just like a fraction of a second of pure agony then it just faded. none of my friends have ever had anything like that. u sure it's not something more serious? also should i take the aspirin and caffeine together right away or wait a bit?",
